title: 820-3115 turns off after a period of time
message: no signs of oxidation.  voltage: PPBUS_g3h 12.59V;  PP3v42_g3h 3.49V;  ALL_SYS 3.33V;  PLT_RESET_L 3.33V.  after a while, the Mac shuts down and the magsafe is out of light.

title: 820-3115 turns off after a period of time
message:
Did you test w/ and w/o battery?
Check SMC_RESET_L when Magsafe light goes off.
